Metadata: Scalemic 12-​hydroxyambliofu​ran and 12-​acetoxyambliofu​ran, five tetracyclic furanoditerpene​s and a furanosesterter​pene from "Spongia" sp

Eight new compounds were isolated from a Western Australian sponge "Spongia" sp., including 12-​hydroxyambliofu​ran (5), its acetate ester 6, five new tetracyclic diterpenes 7 - 11 and the epoxyfuranosest​erterpene carboxylic acid 12. Compounds 5 and 6, each isolated as a 3:1 mixture of enantiomers as determined by a modified Mosher's ester method and chiral lanthanide NMR shift studies, are rare examples of scalemic marine natural products.
